<p>Dr. Philip S. Hench<lb/>
Mayo Clinic<lb/>
Rochester, Minn.<lb/>
Dear Dr. Hench:</p>
<p>Thank you for your letter of September 8. We are<lb/>
looking forward to receiving your telegram on the<lb/>
13th.</p>
<p>I much appreciate your comments concerning Dr.<lb/>
Reed's graduation date. The year '97 in your let-<lb/>
ter was certainly an inadvertent mistake. Our<lb/>
University records show he was graduated in '73.</p>
<p>We have invited General Reed, of whom you spoke,<lb/>
but as yet received no reply. If he does not<lb/>
come, we are in hopes that he too will send us a<lb/>
message.</p>
<closer>
<salute>Yours sincerely,</salute>
<signed>John Whelden</signed>
JW:dh<lb/>
